        <abstract> 
<p>Relates anecdote concerning the blind Henry Fawcett and the Bishop of Oxford; Fawcett proclaimed, within the other’s hearing, that the Bishop had not read the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
